br />\n4 年前黎講佢都 ok 架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驗眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CennVeaWsAAQLOT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCennVeaWsAAQLOT.jpg&h=3ba1edd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O_vOP4PEKRY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FO_vOP4PEKRY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=fe6eb503&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌原來係darling ng<br />\n我記得佢痴住社毛同summer 個陣好似冇咁肥 個陣d人仲吹佢做社運女神<br />\n屌 依家變到成隻emilia wong咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下<br />\nEmilia wong 依家屌打darling、peggy 佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱狗只餘BONIX可以一戰</blockquote><br />\n見得太多老人家身邊有個幾十歲仲痴住佢住，伸手問老豆攞＄使的衰仔。<br />\n但老人家覺得個仔冇工返成日陪住佢好乖。<br />\n最後個衰仔驚自力更新果個收養返來的阿哥會爭家產，日日夜夜響老人身邊講是非<br />\n話阿哥謀佢身家、話阿哥上次幫老人裝冷氣食夾棍、話阿哥唔孝順、話阿哥幫老豆投資果筆＄一定有過水濕腳、話阿哥又唔係親生仔，邊會真心對你好？<br />\n其他平時冇乜往來，睇佢成家唔起嘅三姑六婆又想分一份，紛紛變哂孝子賢孫，圍住老人起勢氹。<br />\n阿哥想息事寧人，點講都生娘不及養娘大，但班孝子賢孫以己度人，就係唔信有人會唔打算分身家，一定要打巢個阿哥。<br />\n最後個結局係點，粵語殘片播哂比你睇la。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n創造力和幻想會嚇你一跳<br />\n小雲同小達好重要</blockquote><br />\n呀達同國師<br />\n<br />\n開心的清算"},{"pid":"f1c2da8dda0cc832e89f8aa65414b363f0391890","tid":282122,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-24-2015/24554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-24-2015%2F24554&d=zhzUYjFy93mj2Ai8xmLBgYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=1cb98cf0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-24-2015/24554</a><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/13/200609_6127e9d2c