.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FO_vOP4PEKRY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=fe6eb503&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌原來係darling ng<br />\n我記得佢痴住社毛同summer 個陣好似冇咁肥 個陣d人仲吹佢做社運女神<br />\n屌 依家變到成隻emilia wong咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下<br />\nEmilia wong 依家屌打darling、peggy 佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱狗只餘BONIX可以一戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以超音鼠先走去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393a154e0abca1fc6bc0f8352ff8475b2111e857","tid":282122,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dd6957739e37dbc50be00efbff90ede30e22d85","tid":282122,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"上次水晶梨話圓菇碌著得清涼得滯教壞佢啲細路先開始睇佢講乜，咪又係迷云耶西師奶一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}